sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_611ea6790f770300f1c33b8ce1050e72
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.LogInterfaceUsage</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description>Used to log the current page viewed by an user.</description><name>LogInterfaceUsage</name><script><![CDATA[var LogInterfaceUsage = Class.create();
LogInterfaceUsage.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	logger : function(){
		return LogInterfaceUsage.logger(this.getParameter('sysparm_url'));
	},
    type: 'LogInterfaceUsage'
});
LogInterfaceUsage.logger = function(url){
	try{
		var parsedURL = LogInterfaceUsage._parseURL(url);
		var interfaceV = parsedURL[1];
		interfaceV = interfaceV.replace(/\//g,"");

		var interfaceRecord = LogInterfaceUsage._getInterface(interfaceV);

		if(!interfaceRecord)
			return;

		var gr = new GlideRecord("u_interface_usage_log");
			gr.initialize();
			gr.u_user = gs.getUserID();
			gr.u_interface = interfaceRecord.sys_id.toString();
			gr.u_page = parsedURL.length==3? parsedURL[2]:"";
			gr.insert();
	}catch(e){gs.log("Error : \n"+JSON.stringify(e,null,4),"Script Include - LogInterfaceUsage");}
};
LogInterfaceUsage._parseURL = function(url){
	var re = /^https:\/\/.*\..{1,3}(\/\w*\/|\/)(.+\.do.*$)?/g;
	return re.exec(url);
};
LogInterfaceUsage._getInterface = function(prefix){
	var gr = new GlideRecord("u_interface");
	return gr.get("u_name",prefix)?gr:null;
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-22 11:32:59</sys_created_on><sys_id>611ea6790f770300f1c33b8ce1050e72</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>LogInterfaceUsage</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_611ea6790f770300f1c33b8ce1050e72</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-22 11:34:30</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
